and raise those security standards in the first place in markets around the world while mechanical hardware is the foundation of our business and will always be at the core of what we do we recognize that the future of the security industry lies in addressing the needs of an increasingly connected world electronic solutions don’t replace our mechanical products – they make them more powerful that’s why our core strength in mechanical security when combined with digital mobile and interconnected electronic solutions – and our expertise in style and design – makes us a leader in our markets privacy statement cookies policy antihuman trafficking statement terms site map  allegion plc   block d iveagh court harcourt road dublin  co dublin ireland registered in ireland with limited liability registered number  allegion is an equal opportunity and affirmative action employer connect with allegion    allegion  us  commercial safety  security partner login locators select by brands select by categories biometrics credentials door control doors and frames electric strikes electrified locks electromagnetic locks electronic locks exit devices key systems mechanical accessories mechanical locks power supplies readers system accessories trade architect authorized distributor integrator locksmith markets healthcare higher education k multifamily government k document library download templates search library support view all support document library knowledge   center idighardware schlage express handnet contact us press enter new series allegion tech talks allegion futurist rob martens explores the latest tech trends and how these innovations are transforming the security industry watch now  new website tell us what you think our website has a fresh new look and has been reimagined to improve your experience how did we do wed love your feedback   submit feedback schlage nd series lock this grade  rated lock is tough durable and fits a wide variety of applications continuous impr