randi to eco schulte gmbh a familyowned german producer of trim and lock products in return allegion will receive a minority  read details allegion plc company info products press release downloads supplier management center links associated with the pages industries brands products  solutions copyright  asmagcom all rights reserved privacy policy magazine company info contact us site map allegion  wikipedia allegion from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from allegion plc jump to navigation search allegion plc type public traded as nyse alle sp  component industry security access control founded  headquarters dublin ireland website httpwwwallegioncom allegion plc is a provider of security products and solutions for homes and businesses it makes  global brands including cisa interflex lcn schlage and von duprin the us billion company employs around  people and sells products in more than  countries across the world allegion spun off from ingersoll rand plc on  december  and became a standalone publicly traded company this placed allegion on the sp  where it replaced jc penney contents  mergers and subsidiaries  ownership  locations  brands and subsidiaries  references  external links mergers and subsidiariesedit on  january  allegion acquired certain assets of schlage lock de colombia sa the second largest mechanical lock manufacturer in colombia with revenues of us  million the acquisition gave allegion a squarefoot integrated plant in bogota colombia and approximately  new employees ownershipedit as of  allegion shares are mainly held by institutional investors t rowe price vanguard group jpmorgan chase and others locationsedit allegion plc is headquartered in dublin ireland its regional offices for the americas is in carmel indiana usa its european regional offices are in faenza italy and the company’s asia headquarters are in tower b of city center of shanghai in shanghai china brands and subsidiariesedit aptiq axa bricard brio briton costruzioni ital